{
  "book": "1nephi",
  "bookName": "1 Nephi",
  "chapter": 13,
  "voice": {
    "provider": "elevenlabs",
    "voice_id": "ddDFRErfhdc2asyySOG5",
    "model_id": "eleven_multilingual_v2",
    "settings": {
      "stability": 0.5,
      "similarity_boost": 0.75,
      "style": 0.35,
      "use_speaker_boost": true
    },
    "name": "Samuel"
  },
  "pauses": {
    "line_ms": 180,
    "verse_ms": 500
  },
  "duration": 680.74,
  "lines": [
    {
      "start": 0.0,
      "end": 2.183,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And then the angel spoke to me, saying:",
      "verse": "13:1",
      "lineIndex": 1
    },
    {
      "start": 2.363,
      "end": 3.199,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Look!",
      "verse": "13:1",
      "lineIndex": 2
    },
    {
      "start": 3.379,
      "end": 6.63,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And I looked and saw many nations and kingdoms.",
      "verse": "13:1",
      "lineIndex": 3
    },
    {
      "start": 7.31,
      "end": 8.935,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And the angel said to me:",
      "verse": "13:2",
      "lineIndex": 4
    },
    {
      "start": 9.115,
      "end": 10.508,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "What do you behold?",
      "verse": "13:2",
      "lineIndex": 5
    },
    {
      "start": 10.688,
      "end": 11.895,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And I said:",
      "verse": "13:2",
      "lineIndex": 6
    },
    {
      "start": 12.075,
      "end": 14.815,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "I behold many nations and kingdoms.",
      "verse": "13:2",
      "lineIndex": 7
    },
    {
      "start": 15.495,
      "end": 16.888,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And he said to me:",
      "verse": "13:3",
      "lineIndex": 8
    },
    {
      "start": 17.068,
      "end": 19.762,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "These are the nations and kingdoms of the Gentiles.",
      "verse": "13:3",
      "lineIndex": 9
    },
    {
      "start": 20.442,
      "end": 23.971,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And then I saw among the nations of the Gentiles",
      "verse": "13:4",
      "lineIndex": 10
    },
    {
      "start": 24.151,
      "end": 26.519,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "the formation of a great church.",
      "verse": "13:4",
      "lineIndex": 11
    },
    {
      "start": 27.199,
      "end": 28.824,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And the angel said to me:",
      "verse": "13:5",
      "lineIndex": 13
    },
    {
      "start": 29.004,
      "end": 31.326,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Behold the formation of a church",
      "verse": "13:5",
      "lineIndex": 14
    },
    {
      "start": 31.506,
      "end": 35.268,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "which is most abominable above all other churches,",
      "verse": "13:5",
      "lineIndex": 15
    },
    {
      "start": 35.448,
      "end": 37.538,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "which kills the saints of God,",
      "verse": "13:5",
      "lineIndex": 16
    },
    {
      "start": 37.718,
      "end": 40.597,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "yes, and tortures them and binds them down,",
      "verse": "13:5",
      "lineIndex": 17
    },
    {
      "start": 40.777,
      "end": 43.331,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and yokes them with a yoke of iron,",
      "verse": "13:5",
      "lineIndex": 18
    },
    {
      "start": 43.511,
      "end": 45.972,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and brings them down into captivity.",
      "verse": "13:5",
      "lineIndex": 19
    },
    {
      "start": 46.652,
      "end": 49.856,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And then I saw this great and abominable church;",
      "verse": "13:6",
      "lineIndex": 20
    },
    {
      "start": 50.036,
      "end": 51.754,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and I saw the devil",
      "verse": "13:6",
      "lineIndex": 21
    },
    {
      "start": 51.934,
      "end": 54.117,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that he was the founder of it.",
      "verse": "13:6",
      "lineIndex": 22
    },
    {
      "start": 54.797,
      "end": 57.165,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And I also saw gold, and silver,",
      "verse": "13:7",
      "lineIndex": 23
    },
    {
      "start": 57.345,
      "end": 60.782,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and silks, and scarlets, and fine-twined linen,",
      "verse": "13:7",
      "lineIndex": 24
    },
    {
      "start": 60.962,
      "end": 63.098,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and all manner of precious clothing;",
      "verse": "13:7",
      "lineIndex": 25
    },
    {
      "start": 63.278,
      "end": 64.996,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and I saw many harlots.",
      "verse": "13:7",
      "lineIndex": 26
    },
    {
      "start": 65.676,
      "end": 67.673,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And the angel spoke to me, saying:",
      "verse": "13:8",
      "lineIndex": 27
    },
    {
      "start": 67.853,
      "end": 69.896,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Behold the gold, and the silver,",
      "verse": "13:8",
      "lineIndex": 28
    },
    {
      "start": 70.076,
      "end": 74.023,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and the silks, and the scarlets, and the fine-twined linen,",
      "verse": "13:8",
      "lineIndex": 29
    },
    {
      "start": 74.203,
      "end": 76.943,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and the precious clothing, and the harlots,",
      "verse": "13:8",
      "lineIndex": 30
    },
    {
      "start": 77.123,
      "end": 80.281,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "are the desires of this great and abominable church.",
      "verse": "13:8",
      "lineIndex": 31
    },
    {
      "start": 80.961,
      "end": 83.422,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And also for the praise of the world",
      "verse": "13:9",
      "lineIndex": 32
    },
    {
      "start": 83.602,
      "end": 85.785,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "do they destroy the saints of God,",
      "verse": "13:9",
      "lineIndex": 33
    },
    {
      "start": 85.965,
      "end": 88.287,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and bring them down into captivity.",
      "verse": "13:9",
      "lineIndex": 34
    },
    {
      "start": 88.967,
      "end": 91.428,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And then I looked and saw many waters;",
      "verse": "13:10",
      "lineIndex": 35
    },
    {
      "start": 91.608,
      "end": 95.184,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and they divided the Gentiles from the seed of my brothers.",
      "verse": "13:10",
      "lineIndex": 36
    },
    {
      "start": 95.864,
      "end": 97.582,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And then the angel said to me:",
      "verse": "13:11",
      "lineIndex": 37
    },
    {
      "start": 97.762,
      "end": 101.152,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Behold the wrath of God is upon the seed of your brothers.",
      "verse": "13:11",
      "lineIndex": 38
    },
    {
      "start": 101.832,
      "end": 104.851,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And I looked and saw a man among the Gentiles,",
      "verse": "13:12",
      "lineIndex": 40
    },
    {
      "start": 105.031,
      "end": 110.047,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "who was separated from the seed of my brothers by the many waters;",
      "verse": "13:12",
      "lineIndex": 41
    },
    {
      "start": 110.227,
      "end": 112.177,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and I saw the Spirit of God,",
      "verse": "13:12",
      "lineIndex": 42
    },
    {
      "start": 112.357,
      "end": 115.143,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that it came down and wrought upon the man;",
      "verse": "13:12",
      "lineIndex": 43
    },
    {
      "start": 115.323,
      "end": 118.017,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and he went forth upon the many waters,",
      "verse": "13:12",
      "lineIndex": 44
    },
    {
      "start": 118.197,
      "end": 120.333,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "even to the seed of my brothers,",
      "verse": "13:12",
      "lineIndex": 45
    },
    {
      "start": 120.513,
      "end": 122.278,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "who were in the promised land.",
      "verse": "13:12",
      "lineIndex": 46
    },
    {
      "start": 122.958,
      "end": 125.094,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And then I saw the Spirit of God,",
      "verse": "13:13",
      "lineIndex": 47
    },
    {
      "start": 125.274,
      "end": 127.596,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "it wrought upon other Gentiles;",
      "verse": "13:13",
      "lineIndex": 48
    },
    {
      "start": 127.776,
      "end": 130.237,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and they went forth out of captivity,",
      "verse": "13:13",
      "lineIndex": 49
    },
    {
      "start": 130.417,
      "end": 132.042,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "upon the many waters.",
      "verse": "13:13",
      "lineIndex": 50
    },
    {
      "start": 132.722,
      "end": 134.208,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And then I saw",
      "verse": "13:14",
      "lineIndex": 51
    },
    {
      "start": 134.388,
      "end": 137.917,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "many multitudes of the Gentiles upon the land of promise;",
      "verse": "13:14",
      "lineIndex": 52
    },
    {
      "start": 138.097,
      "end": 140.094,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and I saw the wrath of God,",
      "verse": "13:14",
      "lineIndex": 53
    },
    {
      "start": 140.274,
      "end": 143.06,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that it was upon the seed of my brothers;",
      "verse": "13:14",
      "lineIndex": 54
    },
    {
      "start": 143.24,
      "end": 146.769,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and they were scattered before the Gentiles and were struck.",
      "verse": "13:14",
      "lineIndex": 55
    },
    {
      "start": 147.449,
      "end": 149.492,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And I saw the Spirit of the Lord,",
      "verse": "13:15",
      "lineIndex": 56
    },
    {
      "start": 149.672,
      "end": 153.062,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that it was upon the Gentiles, and they prospered",
      "verse": "13:15",
      "lineIndex": 57
    },
    {
      "start": 153.242,
      "end": 155.982,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and obtain the land for their inheritance;",
      "verse": "13:15",
      "lineIndex": 58
    },
    {
      "start": 156.162,
      "end": 157.88,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and I saw that they were white,",
      "verse": "13:15",
      "lineIndex": 59
    },
    {
      "start": 158.06,
      "end": 159.918,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and very fair and beautiful,",
      "verse": "13:15",
      "lineIndex": 60
    },
    {
      "start": 160.098,
      "end": 162.606,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "like to my people before they were killed.",
      "verse": "13:15",
      "lineIndex": 61
    },
    {
      "start": 163.286,
      "end": 168.719,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And then I, Nephi, saw that the Gentiles who had gone forth out of captivity",
      "verse": "13:16",
      "lineIndex": 62
    },
    {
      "start": 168.899,
      "end": 171.221,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "humbled themselves before the Lord;",
      "verse": "13:16",
      "lineIndex": 63
    },
    {
      "start": 171.401,
      "end": 173.677,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and the power of the Lord was with them.",
      "verse": "13:16",
      "lineIndex": 64
    },
    {
      "start": 174.357,
      "end": 178.815,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And I saw that their mother Gentiles were gathered together upon the waters,",
      "verse": "13:17",
      "lineIndex": 65
    },
    {
      "start": 178.995,
      "end": 182.014,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and upon the land also, to battle against them.",
      "verse": "13:17",
      "lineIndex": 66
    },
    {
      "start": 182.694,
      "end": 185.341,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And I saw that the power of God was with them,",
      "verse": "13:18",
      "lineIndex": 67
    },
    {
      "start": 185.521,
      "end": 189.236,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and also that the wrath of God was upon all those",
      "verse": "13:18",
      "lineIndex": 68
    },
    {
      "start": 189.416,
      "end": 192.992,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that were gathered together against them to battle.",
      "verse": "13:18",
      "lineIndex": 69
    },
    {
      "start": 193.672,
      "end": 197.666,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And I, Nephi, saw that the Gentiles that had gone out of captivity",
      "verse": "13:19",
      "lineIndex": 70
    },
    {
      "start": 197.846,
      "end": 200.447,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "were delivered by the power of God",
      "verse": "13:19",
      "lineIndex": 71
    },
    {
      "start": 200.627,
      "end": 203.321,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "out of the hands of all other nations.",
      "verse": "13:19",
      "lineIndex": 72
    },
    {
      "start": 204.001,
      "end": 207.577,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And then I, Nephi, saw that they prospered in the land;",
      "verse": "13:20",
      "lineIndex": 73
    },
    {
      "start": 207.757,
      "end": 209.104,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and I saw a book,",
      "verse": "13:20",
      "lineIndex": 74
    },
    {
      "start": 209.284,
      "end": 211.745,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and it was carried forth among them.",
      "verse": "13:20",
      "lineIndex": 75
    },
    {
      "start": 212.425,
      "end": 214.05,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And the angel said to me:",
      "verse": "13:21",
      "lineIndex": 76
    },
    {
      "start": 214.23,
      "end": 216.831,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Do you know the meaning of the book?",
      "verse": "13:21",
      "lineIndex": 77
    },
    {
      "start": 217.511,
      "end": 219.09,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And I said to him:",
      "verse": "13:22",
      "lineIndex": 78
    },
    {
      "start": 219.27,
      "end": 220.477,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "I know not.",
      "verse": "13:22",
      "lineIndex": 79
    },
    {
      "start": 221.157,
      "end": 222.364,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And he said:",
      "verse": "13:23",
      "lineIndex": 81
    },
    {
      "start": 222.544,
      "end": 225.191,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Behold it proceeds out of the mouth of a Jew.",
      "verse": "13:23",
      "lineIndex": 82
    },
    {
      "start": 225.371,
      "end": 227.229,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And I, Nephi, saw it;",
      "verse": "13:23",
      "lineIndex": 83
    },
    {
      "start": 227.409,
      "end": 228.802,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and he said to me:",
      "verse": "13:23",
      "lineIndex": 84
    },
    {
      "start": 228.982,
      "end": 232.558,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "The book that you behold is a record of the Jews,",
      "verse": "13:23",
      "lineIndex": 85
    },
    {
      "start": 232.738,
      "end": 235.617,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "which contains the covenants of the Lord,",
      "verse": "13:23",
      "lineIndex": 86
    },
    {
      "start": 235.797,
      "end": 238.537,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "which he has made to the house of Israel;",
      "verse": "13:23",
      "lineIndex": 87
    },
    {
      "start": 238.717,
      "end": 243.082,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and it also contains many of the prophecies of the holy prophets;",
      "verse": "13:23",
      "lineIndex": 88
    },
    {
      "start": 243.262,
      "end": 245.677,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and it is a record like to the engravings",
      "verse": "13:23",
      "lineIndex": 89
    },
    {
      "start": 245.857,
      "end": 248.04,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "which are upon the plates of brass,",
      "verse": "13:23",
      "lineIndex": 90
    },
    {
      "start": 248.22,
      "end": 250.263,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "save there are not so many;",
      "verse": "13:23",
      "lineIndex": 91
    },
    {
      "start": 250.443,
      "end": 253.415,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "but, they contain the covenants of the Lord,",
      "verse": "13:23",
      "lineIndex": 92
    },
    {
      "start": 253.595,
      "end": 256.335,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "which he has made to the house of Israel;",
      "verse": "13:23",
      "lineIndex": 93
    },
    {
      "start": 256.515,
      "end": 259.394,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "so, they are of great worth to the Gentiles.",
      "verse": "13:23",
      "lineIndex": 94
    },
    {
      "start": 260.074,
      "end": 262.117,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And the angel of the Lord said to me:",
      "verse": "13:24",
      "lineIndex": 95
    },
    {
      "start": 262.297,
      "end": 267.08,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "You have seen that the book proceeded forth from the mouth of a Jew;",
      "verse": "13:24",
      "lineIndex": 96
    },
    {
      "start": 267.26,
      "end": 270.279,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and when it proceeded forth from the mouth of a Jew",
      "verse": "13:24",
      "lineIndex": 97
    },
    {
      "start": 270.459,
      "end": 273.896,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "it contained the fullness of the gospel of the Lord,",
      "verse": "13:24",
      "lineIndex": 98
    },
    {
      "start": 274.076,
      "end": 276.537,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "of whom the twelve apostles bear record;",
      "verse": "13:24",
      "lineIndex": 99
    },
    {
      "start": 276.717,
      "end": 278.342,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and they bear record",
      "verse": "13:24",
      "lineIndex": 100
    },
    {
      "start": 278.522,
      "end": 281.401,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "according to the truth which is in the Lamb of God.",
      "verse": "13:24",
      "lineIndex": 101
    },
    {
      "start": 282.081,
      "end": 285.982,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "So, these things go forth from the Jews in purity to the Gentiles,",
      "verse": "13:25",
      "lineIndex": 102
    },
    {
      "start": 286.162,
      "end": 288.391,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "according to the truth which is in God.",
      "verse": "13:25",
      "lineIndex": 103
    },
    {
      "start": 289.071,
      "end": 293.251,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And after they go forth by the hand of the twelve apostles of the Lamb,",
      "verse": "13:26",
      "lineIndex": 105
    },
    {
      "start": 293.431,
      "end": 295.66,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "from the Jews to the Gentiles,",
      "verse": "13:26",
      "lineIndex": 106
    },
    {
      "start": 295.84,
      "end": 299.787,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "you see the formation of that great and abominable church,",
      "verse": "13:26",
      "lineIndex": 107
    },
    {
      "start": 299.967,
      "end": 303.218,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "which is most abominable above all other churches;",
      "verse": "13:26",
      "lineIndex": 108
    },
    {
      "start": 303.398,
      "end": 307.206,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "for behold, they have taken away from the gospel of the Lamb",
      "verse": "13:26",
      "lineIndex": 109
    },
    {
      "start": 307.386,
      "end": 310.126,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "many parts which are plain and most precious;",
      "verse": "13:26",
      "lineIndex": 110
    },
    {
      "start": 310.306,
      "end": 313.789,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and also many covenants of the Lord have they taken away.",
      "verse": "13:26",
      "lineIndex": 111
    },
    {
      "start": 314.469,
      "end": 315.955,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And all this have they done",
      "verse": "13:27",
      "lineIndex": 112
    },
    {
      "start": 316.135,
      "end": 319.246,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that they might pervert the right ways of the Lord,",
      "verse": "13:27",
      "lineIndex": 113
    },
    {
      "start": 319.426,
      "end": 321.887,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that they might blind the eyes",
      "verse": "13:27",
      "lineIndex": 114
    },
    {
      "start": 322.067,
      "end": 325.039,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and harden the hearts of the children of men.",
      "verse": "13:27",
      "lineIndex": 115
    },
    {
      "start": 325.719,
      "end": 326.787,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "So, you see",
      "verse": "13:28",
      "lineIndex": 116
    },
    {
      "start": 326.967,
      "end": 329.335,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that after the book has gone forth",
      "verse": "13:28",
      "lineIndex": 117
    },
    {
      "start": 329.515,
      "end": 332.905,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "through the hands of the great and abominable church,",
      "verse": "13:28",
      "lineIndex": 118
    },
    {
      "start": 333.085,
      "end": 338.333,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that there are many plain and precious things taken away from the book,",
      "verse": "13:28",
      "lineIndex": 119
    },
    {
      "start": 338.513,
      "end": 340.928,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "which is the book of the Lamb of God.",
      "verse": "13:28",
      "lineIndex": 120
    },
    {
      "start": 341.608,
      "end": 345.184,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And after these plain and precious things were taken away",
      "verse": "13:29",
      "lineIndex": 121
    },
    {
      "start": 345.364,
      "end": 348.754,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "it goes forth to all the nations of the Gentiles;",
      "verse": "13:29",
      "lineIndex": 122
    },
    {
      "start": 348.934,
      "end": 352.324,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and after it goes forth to all the nations of the Gentiles,",
      "verse": "13:29",
      "lineIndex": 123
    },
    {
      "start": 352.504,
      "end": 356.126,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "indeed, even across the many waters which you have seen",
      "verse": "13:29",
      "lineIndex": 124
    },
    {
      "start": 356.306,
      "end": 360.021,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "with the Gentiles which have gone forth out of captivity,",
      "verse": "13:29",
      "lineIndex": 125
    },
    {
      "start": 360.201,
      "end": 363.08,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "you see\u2014 because of the many plain and precious things",
      "verse": "13:29",
      "lineIndex": 126
    },
    {
      "start": 363.26,
      "end": 365.675,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "which have been taken out of the book,",
      "verse": "13:29",
      "lineIndex": 127
    },
    {
      "start": 365.855,
      "end": 370.453,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "which were plain to the understanding of the children of men,",
      "verse": "13:29",
      "lineIndex": 128
    },
    {
      "start": 370.633,
      "end": 373.837,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "according to the plainness which is in the Lamb of God\u2014",
      "verse": "13:29",
      "lineIndex": 129
    },
    {
      "start": 374.017,
      "end": 376.85,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "because of these things which are taken away",
      "verse": "13:29",
      "lineIndex": 130
    },
    {
      "start": 377.03,
      "end": 378.934,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "out of the gospel of the Lamb,",
      "verse": "13:29",
      "lineIndex": 131
    },
    {
      "start": 379.114,
      "end": 381.018,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "a very great many stumble,",
      "verse": "13:29",
      "lineIndex": 132
    },
    {
      "start": 381.198,
      "end": 384.774,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "yes, so much so that Satan has great power over them.",
      "verse": "13:29",
      "lineIndex": 133
    },
    {
      "start": 385.454,
      "end": 387.59,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "But, you behold that the Gentiles",
      "verse": "13:30",
      "lineIndex": 134
    },
    {
      "start": 387.77,
      "end": 390.371,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "who have gone forth out of captivity,",
      "verse": "13:30",
      "lineIndex": 135
    },
    {
      "start": 390.551,
      "end": 395.427,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and have been lifted up by the power of God above all other nations,",
      "verse": "13:30",
      "lineIndex": 136
    },
    {
      "start": 395.607,
      "end": 397.511,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "upon the face of the land",
      "verse": "13:30",
      "lineIndex": 137
    },
    {
      "start": 397.691,
      "end": 399.967,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "which is choice above all other lands,",
      "verse": "13:30",
      "lineIndex": 138
    },
    {
      "start": 400.147,
      "end": 404.652,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "which is the land that the Lord God has covenanted with your father",
      "verse": "13:30",
      "lineIndex": 139
    },
    {
      "start": 404.832,
      "end": 408.222,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that his seed should have for the land of their inheritance;",
      "verse": "13:30",
      "lineIndex": 140
    },
    {
      "start": 408.402,
      "end": 411.235,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "so, you see that the Lord God will not suffer",
      "verse": "13:30",
      "lineIndex": 141
    },
    {
      "start": 411.415,
      "end": 415.362,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that the Gentiles will utterly destroy the mixture of your seed,",
      "verse": "13:30",
      "lineIndex": 142
    },
    {
      "start": 415.542,
      "end": 417.539,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "which are among your brothers.",
      "verse": "13:30",
      "lineIndex": 143
    },
    {
      "start": 418.219,
      "end": 419.844,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Neither will he suffer",
      "verse": "13:31",
      "lineIndex": 144
    },
    {
      "start": 420.024,
      "end": 423.693,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that the Gentiles shall destroy the seed of your brothers.",
      "verse": "13:31",
      "lineIndex": 145
    },
    {
      "start": 424.373,
      "end": 426.416,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Neither will the Lord God suffer",
      "verse": "13:32",
      "lineIndex": 146
    },
    {
      "start": 426.596,
      "end": 431.797,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that the Gentiles shall forever remain in that awful state of blindness,",
      "verse": "13:32",
      "lineIndex": 147
    },
    {
      "start": 431.977,
      "end": 433.835,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "which you behold they are in,",
      "verse": "13:32",
      "lineIndex": 148
    },
    {
      "start": 434.015,
      "end": 438.473,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "because of the plain and most precious parts of the gospel of the Lamb",
      "verse": "13:32",
      "lineIndex": 149
    },
    {
      "start": 438.653,
      "end": 442.09,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "which have been kept back by that abominable church,",
      "verse": "13:32",
      "lineIndex": 150
    },
    {
      "start": 442.27,
      "end": 444.267,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "whose formation you have seen.",
      "verse": "13:32",
      "lineIndex": 151
    },
    {
      "start": 444.947,
      "end": 446.712,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "So saith the Lamb of God:",
      "verse": "13:33",
      "lineIndex": 153
    },
    {
      "start": 446.892,
      "end": 449.121,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "I will be merciful to the Gentiles,",
      "verse": "13:33",
      "lineIndex": 154
    },
    {
      "start": 449.301,
      "end": 454.317,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "to the visiting of the remnant of the house of Israel in great judgment.",
      "verse": "13:33",
      "lineIndex": 155
    },
    {
      "start": 454.997,
      "end": 457.876,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And then the angel of the Lord spoke to me, saying:",
      "verse": "13:34",
      "lineIndex": 156
    },
    {
      "start": 458.056,
      "end": 460.146,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Behold, saith the Lamb of God,",
      "verse": "13:34",
      "lineIndex": 157
    },
    {
      "start": 460.326,
      "end": 463.623,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "after I have visited the remnant of the house of Israel\u2014",
      "verse": "13:34",
      "lineIndex": 158
    },
    {
      "start": 463.803,
      "end": 467.379,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and this remnant of whom I speak is the seed of your father\u2014",
      "verse": "13:34",
      "lineIndex": 159
    },
    {
      "start": 467.559,
      "end": 470.345,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "so, after I have visited them in judgment,",
      "verse": "13:34",
      "lineIndex": 160
    },
    {
      "start": 470.525,
      "end": 473.404,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and struck them by the hand of the Gentiles,",
      "verse": "13:34",
      "lineIndex": 161
    },
    {
      "start": 473.584,
      "end": 476.185,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and after the Gentiles stumble exceedingly,",
      "verse": "13:34",
      "lineIndex": 162
    },
    {
      "start": 476.365,
      "end": 480.312,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "because of the most plain and precious parts of the gospel of the Lamb",
      "verse": "13:34",
      "lineIndex": 163
    },
    {
      "start": 480.492,
      "end": 483.929,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "which have been kept back by that abominable church,",
      "verse": "13:34",
      "lineIndex": 164
    },
    {
      "start": 484.109,
      "end": 485.92,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "which is the mother of harlots,",
      "verse": "13:34",
      "lineIndex": 165
    },
    {
      "start": 486.1,
      "end": 487.772,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "saith the Lamb\u2014",
      "verse": "13:34",
      "lineIndex": 166
    },
    {
      "start": 487.952,
      "end": 490.878,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "I will be merciful to the Gentiles in that day,",
      "verse": "13:34",
      "lineIndex": 167
    },
    {
      "start": 491.058,
      "end": 493.891,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "so much so that I will bring forth to them,",
      "verse": "13:34",
      "lineIndex": 168
    },
    {
      "start": 494.071,
      "end": 495.371,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "in my own power,",
      "verse": "13:34",
      "lineIndex": 169
    },
    {
      "start": 495.551,
      "end": 497.084,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "much of my gospel,",
      "verse": "13:34",
      "lineIndex": 170
    },
    {
      "start": 497.264,
      "end": 499.261,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "which shall be plain and precious,",
      "verse": "13:34",
      "lineIndex": 171
    },
    {
      "start": 499.441,
      "end": 500.834,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "saith the Lamb.",
      "verse": "13:34",
      "lineIndex": 172
    },
    {
      "start": 501.514,
      "end": 503.325,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "For, behold, saith the Lamb:",
      "verse": "13:35",
      "lineIndex": 173
    },
    {
      "start": 503.505,
      "end": 506.059,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "I will manifest myself to your seed,",
      "verse": "13:35",
      "lineIndex": 174
    },
    {
      "start": 506.239,
      "end": 508.747,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that they shall write many things",
      "verse": "13:35",
      "lineIndex": 175
    },
    {
      "start": 508.927,
      "end": 511.295,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "which I shall minister to them,",
      "verse": "13:35",
      "lineIndex": 176
    },
    {
      "start": 511.475,
      "end": 513.936,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "which shall be plain and precious;",
      "verse": "13:35",
      "lineIndex": 177
    },
    {
      "start": 514.116,
      "end": 516.299,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and after your seed shall be destroyed,",
      "verse": "13:35",
      "lineIndex": 178
    },
    {
      "start": 516.479,
      "end": 518.476,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and dwindle in unbelief,",
      "verse": "13:35",
      "lineIndex": 179
    },
    {
      "start": 518.656,
      "end": 520.839,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and also the seed of your brothers,",
      "verse": "13:35",
      "lineIndex": 180
    },
    {
      "start": 521.019,
      "end": 523.248,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "behold, these things shall be hid up,",
      "verse": "13:35",
      "lineIndex": 181
    },
    {
      "start": 523.428,
      "end": 525.657,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "to come forth to the Gentiles,",
      "verse": "13:35",
      "lineIndex": 182
    },
    {
      "start": 525.837,
      "end": 528.484,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "by the gift and power of the Lamb.",
      "verse": "13:35",
      "lineIndex": 183
    },
    {
      "start": 529.164,
      "end": 531.904,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And in them shall be written my gospel,",
      "verse": "13:36",
      "lineIndex": 184
    },
    {
      "start": 532.084,
      "end": 533.477,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "saith the Lamb",
      "verse": "13:36",
      "lineIndex": 185
    },
    {
      "start": 533.657,
      "end": 535.84,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and my rock and my salvation.",
      "verse": "13:36",
      "lineIndex": 186
    },
    {
      "start": 536.52,
      "end": 538.099,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And blessed are they",
      "verse": "13:37",
      "lineIndex": 187
    },
    {
      "start": 538.279,
      "end": 541.344,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "who shall seek to bring forth my Zion at that day,",
      "verse": "13:37",
      "lineIndex": 188
    },
    {
      "start": 541.524,
      "end": 543.521,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "for they shall have the gift",
      "verse": "13:37",
      "lineIndex": 189
    },
    {
      "start": 543.701,
      "end": 545.744,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and the power of the Holy Ghost;",
      "verse": "13:37",
      "lineIndex": 190
    },
    {
      "start": 545.924,
      "end": 547.735,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and if they endure to the end",
      "verse": "13:37",
      "lineIndex": 191
    },
    {
      "start": 547.915,
      "end": 550.376,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "they shall be lifted up at the last day,",
      "verse": "13:37",
      "lineIndex": 192
    },
    {
      "start": 550.556,
      "end": 551.949,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and shall be saved",
      "verse": "13:37",
      "lineIndex": 193
    },
    {
      "start": 552.129,
      "end": 554.683,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "in the everlasting kingdom of the Lamb;",
      "verse": "13:37",
      "lineIndex": 194
    },
    {
      "start": 554.863,
      "end": 556.906,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and whoso shall publish peace,",
      "verse": "13:37",
      "lineIndex": 195
    },
    {
      "start": 557.086,
      "end": 559.036,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "yes, tidings of great joy,",
      "verse": "13:37",
      "lineIndex": 196
    },
    {
      "start": 559.216,
      "end": 561.956,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "how beautiful upon the mountains shall they be.",
      "verse": "13:37",
      "lineIndex": 197
    },
    {
      "start": 562.636,
      "end": 566.165,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And then I saw the remnant of the seed of my brothers,",
      "verse": "13:38",
      "lineIndex": 198
    },
    {
      "start": 566.345,
      "end": 568.806,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and also the book of the Lamb of God,",
      "verse": "13:38",
      "lineIndex": 199
    },
    {
      "start": 568.986,
      "end": 571.633,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "which had proceeded forth from the mouth of the Jew,",
      "verse": "13:38",
      "lineIndex": 200
    },
    {
      "start": 571.813,
      "end": 574.507,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that it came forth from the Gentiles",
      "verse": "13:38",
      "lineIndex": 201
    },
    {
      "start": 574.687,
      "end": 577.102,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "to the remnant of the seed of my brothers.",
      "verse": "13:38",
      "lineIndex": 202
    },
    {
      "start": 577.782,
      "end": 580.011,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And after it had come forth to them",
      "verse": "13:39",
      "lineIndex": 203
    },
    {
      "start": 580.191,
      "end": 581.631,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "I saw other books,",
      "verse": "13:39",
      "lineIndex": 204
    },
    {
      "start": 581.811,
      "end": 584.412,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "which came forth by the power of the Lamb,",
      "verse": "13:39",
      "lineIndex": 205
    },
    {
      "start": 584.592,
      "end": 586.542,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "from the Gentiles to them,",
      "verse": "13:39",
      "lineIndex": 206
    },
    {
      "start": 586.722,
      "end": 589.323,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "to the convincing of the Gentiles",
      "verse": "13:39",
      "lineIndex": 207
    },
    {
      "start": 589.503,
      "end": 592.197,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and the remnant of the seed of my brothers,",
      "verse": "13:39",
      "lineIndex": 208
    },
    {
      "start": 592.377,
      "end": 597.16,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and also the Jews who were scattered upon all the face of the earth,",
      "verse": "13:39",
      "lineIndex": 209
    },
    {
      "start": 597.34,
      "end": 599.244,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that the records of the prophets",
      "verse": "13:39",
      "lineIndex": 210
    },
    {
      "start": 599.424,
      "end": 602.535,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and of the twelve apostles of the Lamb are true.",
      "verse": "13:39",
      "lineIndex": 211
    },
    {
      "start": 603.215,
      "end": 605.212,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And the angel spoke to me, saying:",
      "verse": "13:40",
      "lineIndex": 212
    },
    {
      "start": 605.392,
      "end": 606.878,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "These last records,",
      "verse": "13:40",
      "lineIndex": 213
    },
    {
      "start": 607.058,
      "end": 609.473,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "which you have seen among the Gentiles,",
      "verse": "13:40",
      "lineIndex": 214
    },
    {
      "start": 609.653,
      "end": 612.347,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "shall establish the truth of the first,",
      "verse": "13:40",
      "lineIndex": 215
    },
    {
      "start": 612.527,
      "end": 615.035,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "which are of the twelve apostles of the Lamb,",
      "verse": "13:40",
      "lineIndex": 216
    },
    {
      "start": 615.215,
      "end": 618.837,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and shall make known the plain and precious things",
      "verse": "13:40",
      "lineIndex": 217
    },
    {
      "start": 619.017,
      "end": 621.385,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "which have been taken away from them;",
      "verse": "13:40",
      "lineIndex": 218
    },
    {
      "start": 621.565,
      "end": 625.28,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and shall make known to all kindreds, tongues, and people,",
      "verse": "13:40",
      "lineIndex": 219
    },
    {
      "start": 625.46,
      "end": 628.897,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that the Lamb of God is the Son of the Eternal Father,",
      "verse": "13:40",
      "lineIndex": 220
    },
    {
      "start": 629.077,
      "end": 630.935,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and the Savior of the world;",
      "verse": "13:40",
      "lineIndex": 221
    },
    {
      "start": 631.115,
      "end": 633.251,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and that all men must come to him,",
      "verse": "13:40",
      "lineIndex": 222
    },
    {
      "start": 633.431,
      "end": 635.01,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "or they cannot be saved.",
      "verse": "13:40",
      "lineIndex": 223
    },
    {
      "start": 635.69,
      "end": 638.801,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And they must come according to the words",
      "verse": "13:41",
      "lineIndex": 224
    },
    {
      "start": 638.981,
